scriptLines:
query: 'SELECT
                        am.PID,
                        am."MS SubClass",
                        ms.code AS "MS Zoning",
                        am."Roof Style",
                        am."Roof Matl",
                        am."Exterior 1st",
                        am."Exterior 2nd",
                        am."Mas Vnr Type",
                        am."Mas Vnr Area",
                        t1.code AS "Exter Qual",
                        t2.code AS "Exter Cond",
                        am.Foundation,
                        am.Heating,
                        am."Central Air",
                        am.Electrical,
                        am."1st Flr SF",
                        am."2nd Flr SF",
                        am."Low Qual Fin SF",
                        am."Kitchen AbvGr",
                        t3.code AS "Heating QC",
                        t4.code AS "Kitchen Qual",
                        am."TotRms AbvGrd",
                        am.Functional,
                        am.Fireplaces,
                        am."Fireplace Qu",
                        am."Paved Drive",
                        am."Wood Deck SF",
                        am."Open Porch SF",
                        am."Enclosed Porch",
                        am."3Ssn Porch",
                        am."Screen Porch",
                        am.Fence,
                        fl.bedrooms,
                        fl."Full Bath",
                        fl."Half Bath",
                        (am."1st Flr SF" + am."2nd Flr SF" +  am."Low Qual Fin SF") AS "Gr Liv Area",
                        EXTRACT(Year FROM sp."Sale Date") AS "Yr Sold",
                        EXTRACT(Month FROM sp."Sale Date") AS "Mo Sold"
                    FROM amesdbtemp am
                    INNER JOIN mszoning ms
                        ON am."MS Zoning" = ms.id
                    INNER JOIN typequality t1
                        ON am."Exter Qual" = t1.id
                    INNER JOIN typequality t2
                        ON am."Exter Cond" = t2.id
                    INNER JOIN typequality t3
                        ON am."Heating QC" = t3.id
                    INNER JOIN typequality t4
                        ON am."Kitchen Qual" = t4.id
                    INNER JOIN (SELECT
                                    PID,
                                    SUM(bedrooms) AS bedrooms,
                                    SUM("Full Bath") AS "Full Bath",
                                    SUM("Half Bath") AS "Half Bath"
                                FROM floordetail
                                GROUP BY PID) fl
                        ON am.PID = fl.PID
                    INNER JOIN saleproperty sp
                        ON am.PID = sp.PID',
{Year Remod/Add} = iif(isNull({Year Remod/Add}), {Year Built}, {Year Remod/Add})) ~> ajustenulos
iif(Neighborhood == 'South & West of Iowa State University', 'SWISU',

{Condition 1} = iif({Condition 1} == 'Adjacent to arterial street', 'Artery', iif({Condition 1} == 'Adjacent to feeder street', 'Feedr', iif({Condition 1} == 'Normal', 'Norm', iif({Condition 1} == "Within 200' of North-South Railroad", 'RRNn', iif({Condition 1} == 'Adjacent to North-South Railroad', 'RRAn', iif({Condition 1} == 'Near positive off-site feature--park greenbelt etc.', 'PosN', iif({Condition 1} == 'Adjacent to postive off-site feature', 'PosA', iif({Condition 1} == "Within 200' of East-West Railroad", 'RRNe', iif({Condition 1} == 'Adjacent to East-West Railroad', 'RRAe', 'NA'))))))))),

{Lot Shape} = iif({Lot Shape} == 'Regular', 'Reg', iif({Lot Shape} == 'Slightly irregular', 'IR1', iif({Lot Shape} == 'Moderately Irregular', 'IR2', iif({Lot Shape} == 'Irregular', 'IR3', 'NA'))))) ~> transformacion
